{"tid":2111974,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【會師中環】制裁是對林鄭的肯定 - 神仙丁","createTime":"2020-07-17T03:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T03:09:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"23b101e2f5d47f9425c2c313d3826e7130540c79","tid":2111974,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:06:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200717/EGJF3D75T43KA6W4OOS5ZCDIOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200717%2FEGJF3D75T43KA6W4OOS5ZCDIOY%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=bf437ebf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200717%2FEGJF3D75T43KA6W4OOS5ZCDIOY%2F&h=03d3f2a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200717/EGJF3D75T43KA6W4OOS5ZCDIOY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【會師中環】制裁是對林鄭的肯定 - 神仙丁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6OlVLWsysMAIPRcUDwKV8X68cMM=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CU55AMKQMT675CLZYJQSNH7H74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6OlVLWsysMAIPRcUDwKV8X68cMM%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCU55AMKQMT675CLZYJQSNH7H74.jpg&h=1175e504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自國安法通過後，香港成功變「一中一制」，林鄭應該很高興。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n自從國安法通過後，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。香港這次成功「二次回歸」，外界反應完美貫切「一中原則」，我想對香港以至大陸政府來講，都可說是求仁得仁，他們實在應該高興才對。<br />\n<br />\n「一國兩制」本。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港政府的政策和演變，很多都是跟着這條主軸去發展。由遠的每日150單程證人口融合、到近年大灣區的經濟融合、立法會霸王硬上弓的政制融合、警察執法的維穩融合、學術自由的教育融合，政府每一步都朝着全面回歸的方向去走。國安法的法治融合只不過是最後一根稻草，但肯定不是唯一一條。但換個角度來看，做了這麼久的融合工程，到今天終於換來國際制裁，「一中一制」的大一統戰略都算是獲得敵人的全面認同，抱着「敵人反對我贊成」的精神，難度不值得高興嗎？<br />\n<br />\n神仙丁<br />\n《審計搵丁》負責人<br />\n<a href=\"http://facebook.com/AuditSlave/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FAuditSlave%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=e453cc50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/AuditSlave/</a><br />\n本欄逢周五刊出"},{"pid":"7fa7eb4316ce89741c6623a7299b2a2d9ba272bd","tid":2111974,"uid":261470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"咁快d俾肯定佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}